%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_floatize, udf_dt2d, udf_dt2t
df = uv_band.withColumn('uvi_band', udf_floatize('uvi_band'))\
            .groupby('datetime').avg('uvi_band').sort('datetime')\
            .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi_band)', 'uvi_band')\
            .withColumn('date', udf_dt2d('datetime'))\
            .withColumn('time', udf_dt2t('datetime')).drop('datetime')

paragraphs.title: 10min
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyjake.basemodule import udf_10min

df3 = df.join(df2, ['date', 'time']).withColumn('time', udf_10min('time'))\
        .groupby('date', 'time').avg('uvi_band', 'uvi')\
        .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi_band)', 'uvi_band')\
        .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi)', 'uvi')\
        .sort('date', 'time')
df3.show()
df3.createOrReplaceTempView('uvi_compare_10m')

%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType

udf_30min = udf(lambda s: s[:-2] + ('00' if int(int(s[3:]) / 30) == 0 else '30'))
udf_f = udf(lambda s: float(s), DoubleType())

df_uv = uv_band.withColumn('30min', udf_30min('_c0'))\
               .withColumn('band', udf_f('_c1'))\
               .withColumn('cas', udf_f('_c2'))\
               .withColumn('calib', udf_f('_c3'))\
               .drop('_c0', '_c1', '_c2', '_c3')
df_uv = df_uv.groupby('30min').avg('cas', 'band', 'calib')\
             .withColumnRenamed('avg(cas)', 'cas')\
             .withColumnRenamed('avg(band)', 'band')\
             .withColumnRenamed('avg(calib)', 'calib')\
             .sort('30min')
df_uv.show()
df_uv.createOrReplaceTempView('df_uv')

%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.functions import udf
from pyspark.sql.types import StringType

udf_dt = udf(lambda d, t: d + ' ' + t)
udf_month = udf(lambda d: d.split('-')[1])

nt = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/nt_srs.parquet')
uv = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv_srs.parquet')
cl = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///dayday/clean_days.parquet')
# cl.sort(cl.date.desc()).show()

df_ntuv = nt.join(uv, ['date', 'time'])\
            .join(cl, 'date')\
            .withColumn('datetime', udf_dt('date', 'time'))\
            .withColumn('month', udf_month('datetime'))\
            .select('datetime', 'month', 'illum', 'cct', 'uvb', 'euvb', 'uvi')
df_ntuv.show()
df_ntuv.write.mode('overwrite').parquet('hdfs:///tmp/ntuv.parquet')
